nodes.text: Fillorean was a Supreme Chancellor of the Old Republic circa 15,500 BBY.

It was during his time that the Republic first made contact with the Duinuogwuins, resulting in the Duinuogwuin Contention being fought on Coruscant. When peace was achieved, Fillorean and Borz'Mat'oh founded the University of Coruscant.
The Chancellor Fillorean, a luxury liner, existed millennia after Fillorean's time as chancellor.
